{"article_id":"k4etLJafAwRwm6js","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Trump administration told a federal appeals court Monday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"it thinks","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"all of Obamacare is unconstitutional ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"marking an escalation in its fight against the 2010 law .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Justice Department lawyers previously had argued","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"if the courts found","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Obamacare ' s \" individual mandate \" is no longer constitutional ,","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"then a narrow slice of the program","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"- consumer protections for people with pre-existing conditions -","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"could not stand , either .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"A federal judge in Texas went much further in a December ruling ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"agreeing with plaintiff states","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"who said","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"the whole law should be invalidated .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"On Monday , administration lawyers said","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"they ' re fine with that .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"\" The Department of Justice has determined","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"that the district court ' s judgment should be affirmed , \"","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"they wrote to the 5th U.S . Circuit U.S. Court of Appeals .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Underscoring that point ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"they ' re not urging the court to reverse any of U.S. District Court Judge Reed O ' Connor ' s decision .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"The administration ' s position will breathe new life into the never-ending battle over Obamacare .","depth":3},{"id":23,"text":"Democrats say","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"the administration is playing with fire","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"by refusing to defend the federal health care law against the suit ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"which was filed last year by more than a dozen Republican-led states .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"They say","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"President Trump is leveraging the courts","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to try and secure the full Obamacare repeal","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"that eluded him in 2017 ,","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"despite having a GOP-led Congress .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"\" Tonight in federal court , the Trump administration decided not only to try to destroy protections for Americans","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"living with pre-existing conditions","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"but to declare all-out war on the health care of the American people , \"","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi said late Monday .","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"Mr. Trump has found ways","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"to chip away at parts of Obamacare .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"Most notably , he urged Republicans to zero out Obamacare ' s mandate penalty","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"for shirking insurance","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"when it passed its tax overhaul .","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"State GOP plaintiffs seized on that change ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"reasoning","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"if the mandate is no longer collecting money ,","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"is it no longer a \" tax \"","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"as Chief Justice John G. Roberts said","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"when upholding the health law in 2012 .","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"Blue-state attorneys general have argued in court","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"the mandate is still on the books","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"and , furthermore , Congress clearly intended to leave the rest of the law alone","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"when it gutted the mandate .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"The simmering debate played a pivotal role in the midterm elections .","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"Democrats said","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"the GOP didn ' t have a backup plan","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"if the lawsuit succeeded ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"citing their previous failure","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"to replace the law with something better .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"Democrats retook the House .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"Yet Josh Hawley ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"who joined the anti-Obamacare lawsuit as Missouri ' s attorney general ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"defeated Sen. Claire McCaskill on election night","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"and is now a sitting senator .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"The administration ' s decision","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"to fully back the lawsuit","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"will loom large on Tuesday","depth":5},{"id":66,"text":"when Democrats plan to propose measures","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"that would make Obamacare more generous","depth":6},{"id":68,"text":"and combat Mr. Trump ' s changes to the program ,","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"which they ' ve dubbed \" sabotage . \"","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"Democrats are looking to regain their political footing , anyway ,","depth":4},{"id":71,"text":"as Mr. Trump taunts them over the results of special counsel Robert Mueller ' s two-year investigation ,","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"which found no collusion between his campaign and Russian meddlers .","depth":6},{"id":73,"text":"\" The Barr summary clearly demonstrates","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"that Republicans are trying to take your healthcare away , \"","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"Sen Brian Schatz , Hawaii Democrat , tweeted","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"- a wry allusion to Attorney General William Barr ' s summary of the Mueller findings .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"Yet Mr. Trump appears ready to dig in for a fight over health care , too .","depth":3},{"id":78,"text":"He ' s fumed in recent weeks over late Sen. John McCain ' s decision","depth":5},{"id":79,"text":"to give GOP repeal plans a thumbs down in 2017 ,","depth":5},{"id":80,"text":"and the White House ' s fiscal 2020 budget says","depth":5},{"id":81,"text":"Obamacare should be replaced with fixed grants","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"that allow states to spend federal health","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":165,"left":145,"right":164,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":105,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":104,"right":22,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":86,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":85,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":0,"right":84,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":84,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":103,"left":92,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":4,"right":91,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":91,"left":5,"right":90,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":90,"left":87,"right":89,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":87,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":89,"left":88,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":88,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":95,"right":101,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":11,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":12,"right":93,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":101,"left":96,"right":100,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":96,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":100,"left":98,"right":99,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":97,"right":19,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity